{
  "stem": "16245.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, obviously, for instance, as I mentioned, my brother was chucked out of the Army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All Jews were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were put in labor battalions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then they made it very difficult for Jews to own businesses in their own name.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But of course, they tolerated Jews owning businesses under a Christian name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of this was a slap to the Germans who were pressing the Hungarian government to enact more and more stringent anti-Jewish laws.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they weren't really enforced all that intolerantly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, from the beginning of the war right up to the German occupation in '44.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was tightened all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, there were Jewish members of parliament.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now obviously they were chucked out of parliament.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the end, before the German occupation, even the vote was taken away from Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So in actual fact, the Jews ceased to be citizens of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But nobody took that too seriously.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it had no effect on us, on our daily lives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you-- you're a little bit ahead of yourself there because, really, before you get to the Arrow Cross, you would have to speak of the German occupation that made it possible.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we lived a really quite an idyllic existence in Hungary up to March 19, 1944.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or certainly in comparison to Polish Jews, who were being murdered left, right, and center, we were going to the opera, to concerts, to theater, on holidays, as if the war wouldn't have been on.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Hungary at that time was still neutral.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when the Germans occupied the country, that's when the trouble really started.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very soon, within weeks, Jews were compelled to wear the yellow star, which made movement without false papers impossible.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
